                                 Node: host=localhost port=58070 dbname=regression
                                 ->  Limit
                                       ->  Sort
                                             Sort Key: (random())
                                             ->  Sample Scan on documents_7001_70004 collection
                                                   Sampling: system_rows ('3'::bigint)
   Task Count: 1
   Tasks Shown: All
   ->  Task
         Node: host=localhost port=58070 dbname=regression
         ->  Function Scan on read_intermediate_result intermediate_result
(20 rows)

